"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"干净整洁的交易风格，优秀的交易逻辑和体验使得Arrow成为下一代期权市场应该有的样子。其民主化了整个期权交易管道，从做市到经纪，再到清算和结算。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BAbHax3MJmgL0EWZxQQw9.png?height=497&width=1329)\\n\\n**准备**\\n\\n1\\\\.雪崩测试网（连上网页自动添加并切换）\\n\\n2\\\\.领取测试币（AVAX ）\\n\\n[https://faucet.avax-test.network/](https://faucet.avax-test.network/)\\n\\n**进入网站**\\n\\n[https://fuji-beta.arrow.markets/trading](https://fuji-beta.arrow.markets/trading)\\n\\n![网页右上角连接钱包（自动切换雪崩测试网络）](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4VswAfqWEMUF5HicUTzz5.png?height=582&width=1337)\\n\\n![点击MINT USDC](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/tlDWz7FXU0S6dR8hm_EyQ.png?height=587&width=1338)\\n\\n![钱包确认](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DNxJZUjYRQwuTcktnu-4f.png?height=358&width=764)\\n\\n![币种选择AVAX](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nQUoiT0W2p9JjiZ6Kxm8L.png?height=482&width=1285)\\n\\n![这里是开仓前的选择信息 包括AVAX价格 价格日期 开仓数量](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nq9wYYVPfOepbUeAzacKV.png?height=228&width=1278)\\n\\n![这里包含了当前交易的详细信息（注意按图开仓有可能失败 建议调整行权周期为一个月以上）](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/oDeBWDzcekkfk4fMXR6fO.png?height=522&width=1275)\\n\\n![点击接受](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/eF0AV3ETCZ9YE89nrGsOb.png?height=544&width=1279)\\n\\n![钱包签名](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WeO6spAp-dy-5VT8pdsdl.png?height=358&width=778)\\n\\n![钱包确认](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/yuWfrGif6R6RojzpvYe7a.png?height=316&width=776)\\n\\n![提示开仓成功 返回主界面](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/TA5KJdjj8tizcx0qWwU-f.png?height=481&width=1279)\\n\\n![我们按照需求买入看跌期权](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9w_CY7Aq2SZpE4nfbhEM4.png?height=238&width=1292)\\n\\n![确认期权信息 确认交易 ](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hyA1w103VC0jo0WREVsbk.png?height=492&width=1283)\\n\\n![提示开仓成功 返回主界面](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/psX3KI-ko9guFqlH2fcEG.png?height=432&width=1279)\\n\\n![点击蓝色图标](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hFfoHA8iGNEnXEr8NdeI0.png?height=377&width=1340)\\n\\n![可以查看已开期权的详细情况](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/k_hzzN97xNxo07MIZPc9K.png?height=515&width=1276)\\n\\n![交易记录](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LfQGFuyr28TUoNta-w-6R.png?height=301&width=1257)\\n\\n![买卖操作](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ovbh14Q5gjqFRXk9X8KHx.png?height=243&width=1279)\\n\\n![还可以 操作ETH BTC LINK等期权](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pLRr0ylulabXiu9hL7_qF.png?height=554&width=1298)\\n\\n以上就是Arrow期权协议的简单交互步骤\\n\\n期权标的任意选择 开仓数量任意即可\",\"timestamp\":1641999160,\"title\":\"Arrow期权协议测试网教程\"},\"digest\":\"jG9N3hpiR67PyQ7ds4_fdTpBq80d8m5BlPsoz6xE1os\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x83E8DF8ddf3cd5b51caFFB337B321467225d4650\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jr_WOfSpNlWNak9xu3ZMgTGhL1w1FxrIYF2Sy8NDdT0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"GOXMn6EG_gLZMAy8FB729CCiatncFQZH6yhnDr6h-tw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"N29KTvBNIQQ5unt-hiqg0rOdZtsmPs4Qhe8yPvSDZDb9-3Jv38wTzg11E2y1zmzbGVxdBf5KqZDgu4dPCKaFHw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd091e653731c4db4ef61e4fe71571a122c595b560e590fed8a2dd9a6f3e191d2683597a03ce4850a04eb41e18224f61d851774cf3438376e056b26b2604bc3eb1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jr_WOfSpNlWNak9xu3ZMgTGhL1w1FxrIYF2Sy8NDdT0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"GOXMn6EG_gLZMAy8FB729CCiatncFQZH6yhnDr6h-tw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"jG9N3hpiR67PyQ7ds4_fdTpBq80d8m5BlPsoz6xE1os\"}"